01:20:04.170 --> 01:20:09.650 align:middle line:84%
when X is in A minus A over A
minus A, and X plus 1 is not.

01:20:09.650 --> 01:20:12.410 align:middle line:84%
You use that to show that some
projection of the original set

01:20:12.410 --> 01:20:13.210 align:middle line:90%
