01:20:13.210 --> 01:20:15.517 align:middle line:90%
AUDIENCE: OK.

01:20:15.517 --> 01:20:17.350 align:middle line:84%
PABLO SHMERKIN: This
is a very similar idea,

01:20:17.350 --> 01:20:20.530 align:middle line:84%
except that you have to fight
